  "description": "<p>Our multi-functional eyebrow brush set contains Cyclopentasiloxane, Cyclohexasiloxane, and Trimethylsiloxysilicate. It can fill in eyebrows and enhance the clarity of any makeup look. The angled eyebrow brush is designed with soft synthetic fibers, which better adapt to the use of mixed products. The usage is very simple: trim excess eyebrows with tweezers. Open the eyebrow cream, apply an appropriate amount with a sponge, and adjust the details with the double-ended precision brush. The multi-functional eyebrow brush set comes in three color options, is waterproof and sweat-proof, and has strong staying power. The eyebrow gel creates a naturally perfect eyebrow shape, saving time, and is worth having!<br/></p><p><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/a91c7f91-33e2-4c1b-bcc4-1936ec6d9a70.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/cf029e0b-fa86-4e23-8fad-6c56a8bc3088.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/3396e9ce-e4a2-40a9-bdda-b53727ff555d.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/50dc7219-a2e7-4d67-810c-3b723b4af003.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/0f3fe494-c969-4903-aae9-c4d0d91bfddd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/></p>",
